    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[I]n nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1986" key="#Princeps">Sico</persName> Dei previdentia
                        Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/3499"
                            >Radichis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldii</rs> fidelis nostri, vobis
                            <persName ref="#people/1976">Adelgise</persName> filia sancte
                        recordationis domni <persName key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/303">Arichis</persName>, integram <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><rs key="#Houses">casam</rs> et <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs></rs>
                        infra hanc <placeName key="#Cities #Houses #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventanam</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>, que dicitur Curte Minorem; est enim <rs
                            key="#Fines">fine</rs> fine <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterii Sancte Sophie</orgName> et et &lt;sic>
                        fine platea maiore et fine andito qui vadit ante regias <persName
                            key="#Marepahis" ref="#people/3601">Alahis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marepahis">maripahis</rs> usque in platea; in ea videlicet ratione
                        ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum predicta casa cum
                        integris finibus suis tu et heredes tui habere et possidere valeatis et
                        quicquid de eadem iudicare vel disponere volueris in tua sit potestate
                        iudicandi qualiter volueris, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptus
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary" ref="#people/3602">Theodericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> primo anno, mense novembrio per
                        indictionem undecimam. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
